==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Assayer
<hw>As*say"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who assays. Specifically: One
who examines metallic ores or compounds, for the purpose of determining
the amount of any particular metal in the same, especially of gold or
silver.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Assaying</ent>⟦br⟧
